<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:02:01.290 --> 00:02:03.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000005
00:02:08.510 --> 00:02:10.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The royal capital's in sight.</b></Default>

c0000006
00:02:10.630 --> 00:02:12.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They’re celebrating
the triumphant return</b></Default>

c0000007
00:02:12.510 --> 00:02:13.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of their heroes.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:02:13.590 --> 00:02:15.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can feel the excitement
from here.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:02:15.350 --> 00:02:17.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wheels rattling]</b></Default>

c0000010
00:02:18.100 --> 00:02:20.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] We'll have to start
looking for work soon.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:02:20.850 --> 00:02:23.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're already concerned
about employment?</b></Default>

c0000012
00:02:23.430 --> 00:02:24.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As we all should be.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:02:25.070 --> 00:02:26.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Slaying the Demon King
was one chapter,</b></Default>

c0000014
00:02:27.070 --> 00:02:28.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but read on,</b></Default>

c0000015
00:02:28.900 --> 00:02:31.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for we've stories yet to tell
and lives yet to live.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:31.820 --> 00:02:33.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Lives full of work.</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:33.820 --> 00:02:36.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would take any job
they let me drink on.</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:36.370 --> 00:02:37.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
Very priestly, sir.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:37.870 --> 00:02:40.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all laughing]</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:40.290 --> 00:02:41.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose you're right.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:44.120 --> 00:02:47.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren, the life
that lies ahead of you</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:47.460 --> 00:02:49.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will be far longer
than the rest of us could know</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:49.800 --> 00:02:51.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or that we could begin
to comprehend.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:52.380 --> 00:02:53.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, perhaps.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:53.710 --> 00:02:55.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000026
00:03:08.570 --> 00:03:11.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

c0000027
00:03:15.870 --> 00:03:16.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000028
00:03:17.330 --> 00:03:20.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

c0000029
00:03:30.960 --> 00:03:32.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KING]
Himmel the Hero.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:03:32.840 --> 00:03:34.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Eisen the Warrior.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:03:34.630 --> 00:03:36.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Heiter the Priest.</b></Default>

c0000032
00:03:36.550 --> 00:03:38.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And Frieren the Mage.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:39.550 --> 00:03:41.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have
our wholehearted thanks</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:41.100 --> 00:03:42.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for defeating the Demon King.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:42.930 --> 00:03:45.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your efforts
have launched our world</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:45.190 --> 00:03:47.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into an age of prosperity
and peace.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:48.020 --> 00:03:49.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fireworks]</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:55.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:55.740 --> 00:03:58.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[children laughing]</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:59.450 --> 00:04:00.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000041
00:04:00.950 --> 00:04:01.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My.</b></Default>

c0000042
00:04:03.200 --> 00:04:05.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rumor has it that the King
is going to erect statues</b></Default>

c0000043
00:04:05.710 --> 00:04:06.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of us in the plaza.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:04:07.500 --> 00:04:10.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though, I doubt they'll be able
to capture the complexities</b></Default>

c0000045
00:04:10.500 --> 00:04:12.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of my good looks
in a piece of stone.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:04:12.420 --> 00:04:14.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How I pity the poor sculptor.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:04:15.050 --> 00:04:16.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a self-serving tribute.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:04:16.840 --> 00:04:18.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When we left,
he was only willing</b></Default>

c0000049
00:04:18.390 --> 00:04:20.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to offer up ten copper coins.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:04:20.390 --> 00:04:21.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[slurps]
-[chomps]</b></Default>

c0000051
00:04:22.050 --> 00:04:23.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aw, don't keep your head
in the past.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:04:24.090 --> 00:04:25.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tonight,
the gallant adventurers</b></Default>

c0000053
00:04:25.770 --> 00:04:26.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>drink for free!</b></Default>

c0000054
00:04:26.900 --> 00:04:29.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would say that makes us even,
wouldn't you?</b></Default>

c0000055
00:04:29.190 --> 00:04:30.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not a corrupt priest.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:04:30.600 --> 00:04:33.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

c0000057
00:04:36.070 --> 00:04:38.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000058
00:04:38.360 --> 00:04:40.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's over, isn't it?</b></Default>

c0000059
00:04:41.030 --> 00:04:42.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Indeed.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:04:43.110 --> 00:04:45.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is the moment
our grand adventure ends.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:46.540 --> 00:04:47.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ten years together.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:48.460 --> 00:04:50.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've been through the thick,
the thin, and then some.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:52.210 --> 00:04:53.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The day we departed,</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:53.920 --> 00:04:56.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himmel and Eisen's disrespect
toward the King</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:56.090 --> 00:04:58.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>landed them moments away
from execution.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:58.760 --> 00:05:00.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One misstep, and our journey
would've ended there.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:05:00.970 --> 00:05:02.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm. Mm-hmm.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:05:02.840 --> 00:05:03.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you remember the time</b></Default>

c0000069
00:05:03.930 --> 00:05:06.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Heiter's bottle ache
rendered him all but useless?</b></Default>

c0000070
00:05:08.230 --> 00:05:09.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000071
00:05:11.020 --> 00:05:13.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've gone nearly as pallid
as an undead.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:05:13.440 --> 00:05:14.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you passing?</b></Default>

c0000073
00:05:14.600 --> 00:05:16.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Yes.
-Alas, a shame indeed.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:05:16.570 --> 00:05:19.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] Hm. That was
a weekly occurrence.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:05:19.570 --> 00:05:20.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[laughs]
-Well, I was exceptional</b></Default>

c0000076
00:05:20.820 --> 00:05:21.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in every way.</b></Default>

c0000077
00:05:21.820 --> 00:05:23.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] We debated
leaving you behind</b></Default>

c0000078
00:05:23.400 --> 00:05:25.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when you fell
for that mimic, you know.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:05:25.500 --> 00:05:27.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We repeatedly told her
it was a trap</b></Default>

c0000080
00:05:27.120 --> 00:05:28.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and yet here we are.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:05:28.290 --> 00:05:29.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Is it time to lose the elf?</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:30.120 --> 00:05:33.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all laughing]</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:34.880 --> 00:05:35.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looking back,</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:36.420 --> 00:05:38.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>our memories
sound terrible, don't they?</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:38.550 --> 00:05:39.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:39.970 --> 00:05:40.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
But I had fun.</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:41.880 --> 00:05:44.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You made this quest
the journey of my lifetime.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:44.300 --> 00:05:45.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you, all.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:45.930 --> 00:05:47.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feel the same way.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:47.680 --> 00:05:49.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our adventure
was a mere ten years.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:50.350 --> 00:05:51.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"A mere ten?"</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:51.640 --> 00:05:54.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But that's a full decade
spent on one job.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:05:54.350 --> 00:05:55.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, look at Heiter.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:05:55.690 --> 00:05:58.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's turned into an old man
right before our eyes.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:05:58.110 --> 00:05:59.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not nice.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:05:59.740 --> 00:06:00.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He always looked like that.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:06:01.360 --> 00:06:02.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even less nice.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:06:03.740 --> 00:06:04.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chomps]</b></Default>

c0000099
00:06:06.120 --> 00:06:07.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000100
00:06:07.450 --> 00:06:09.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000101
00:06:09.660 --> 00:06:10.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's nearly time.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:06:11.660 --> 00:06:14.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000103
00:06:19.340 --> 00:06:21.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're here on a special night.
How enchanting.</b></Default>

c0000104
00:06:22.590 --> 00:06:25.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] The Era Meteor shower
happens once every 50 years.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:06:26.640 --> 00:06:28.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our era of peace
couldn't be welcomed</b></Default>

c0000106
00:06:28.600 --> 00:06:29.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in a more perfect way.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:06:29.770 --> 00:06:32.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000108
00:06:32.810 --> 00:06:33.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
Beautiful.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:06:34.020 --> 00:06:36.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] The view from inside
the city isn't very good.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:06:36.730 --> 00:06:38.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] I'm trying
to have a moment here.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:06:38.570 --> 00:06:39.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't spoil the mood.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:06:39.690 --> 00:06:41.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:42.030 --> 00:06:43.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Next time, then.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:06:43.570 --> 00:06:44.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000115
00:06:44.950 --> 00:06:46.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know a good place.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:06:46.410 --> 00:06:48.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll take us there
when the opportunity arises</b></Default>

c0000117
00:06:48.620 --> 00:06:49.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in 50 years.</b></Default>

c0000118
00:06:50.870 --> 00:06:52.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000119
00:06:53.080 --> 00:06:54.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-What's wrong?
-Nothing.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:06:55.590 --> 00:06:56.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing in the world.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:06:58.590 --> 00:06:59.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, it's a plan.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:07:00.300 --> 00:07:01.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fifty years from now.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:07:01.840 --> 00:07:04.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000124
00:07:15.360 --> 00:07:18.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[bird chirping]</b></Default>

c0000125
00:07:24.440 --> 00:07:25.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose I should be leaving.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:07:26.700 --> 00:07:28.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mapped out your next adventure?</b></Default>

c0000127
00:07:28.780 --> 00:07:31.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For the next 100 years,
give or take.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:07:31.370 --> 00:07:33.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I intend to travel
around the central lands</b></Default>

c0000129
00:07:33.370 --> 00:07:34.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>collecting new spells.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:07:34.950 --> 00:07:36.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I'll be sure to stop by.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:07:42.380 --> 00:07:44.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The way elves see this world
is a mystery.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:07:45.100 --> 00:07:47.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who knows how long she's been
a part of it by now?</b></Default>

c0000133
00:07:48.600 --> 00:07:51.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER] In her eyes,
50 or even 100 years</b></Default>

c0000134
00:07:51.510 --> 00:07:53.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>must look like
a trifling thing.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:07:54.220 --> 00:07:56.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000136
00:08:03.150 --> 00:08:06.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

c0000137
00:08:08.120 --> 00:08:10.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000138
00:08:40.020 --> 00:08:43.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[water burbling]</b></Default>

c0000139
00:08:44.270 --> 00:08:45.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE SHOPKEEPER 1A]
Shadow dragon horns?</b></Default>

c0000140
00:08:46.360 --> 00:08:48.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm afraid we don't have
anything like that here.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:08:49.070 --> 00:08:50.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The last time I saw
a shadow dragon</b></Default>

c0000142
00:08:50.950 --> 00:08:52.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>must've been a few decades ago.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:08:52.990 --> 00:08:54.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah. How unfortunate.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:08:55.330 --> 00:08:56.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I needed one for summoning.</b></Default>

c0000145
00:08:59.710 --> 00:09:00.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Come to think of it,</b></Default>

c0000146
00:09:00.710 --> 00:09:02.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I took a horn
from the Demon King's Castle.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:09:03.500 --> 00:09:04.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I asked Himmel to store it.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:09:05.680 --> 00:09:07.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
You do see that it's exuding</b></Default>

c0000149
00:09:07.260 --> 00:09:09.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>some sort of evil aura,
don't you?</b></Default>

c0000150
00:09:09.090 --> 00:09:10.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that dangerous to people?</b></Default>

c0000151
00:09:10.680 --> 00:09:11.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Uh, I don't know.</b></Default>

c0000152
00:09:12.180 --> 00:09:13.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's awfully reassuring.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:09:14.590 --> 00:09:15.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
The Era Meteor Shower</b></Default>

c0000154
00:09:15.890 --> 00:09:17.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>should be circling around soon.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:09:17.390 --> 00:09:18.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll pick up the horn
when I visit.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:09:19.020 --> 00:09:22.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wheels rattling]</b></Default>

c0000157
00:09:22.100 --> 00:09:24.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000158
00:09:25.060 --> 00:09:27.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The city's changed a fair bit
since I was here last.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:09:28.860 --> 00:09:30.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[quacking]
-[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000160
00:09:32.490 --> 00:09:35.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ducks quacking]</b></Default>

c0000161
00:09:37.830 --> 00:09:38.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[bird chirping]</b></Default>

c0000162
00:09:42.790 --> 00:09:44.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It should be
somewhere around here.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:09:45.550 --> 00:09:46.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000164
00:09:47.630 --> 00:09:48.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himmel, is that...?</b></Default>

