<Default><b>[bell ringing]</b></Default>

c0000265
00:15:32.810 --> 00:15:34.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scraping]</b></Default>

c0000266
00:15:37.230 --> 00:15:38.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
In all truthfulness,</b></Default>

c0000267
00:15:39.190 --> 00:15:40.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hardly knew
