c0000268
00:15:41.360 --> 00:15:43.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scraping]</b></Default>

c0000269
00:15:53.620 --> 00:15:54.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ten years with him.</b></Default>

