you're looking for?</b></Default>

c0000330
00:19:20.990 --> 00:19:24.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. I'm trying to locate
the home of a man named Heiter.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:19:25.120 --> 00:19:27.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see, so you're a visitor.</b></Default>

c0000332
00:19:30.590 --> 00:19:32.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] The corrupt priest
is slow to die.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:19:32.630 --> 00:19:33.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Heiter laughs]</b></Default>

c0000334
00:19:34.300 --> 00:19:35.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Turns out a stylish exit</b></Default>

c0000335
00:19:36.010 --> 00:19:37.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is harder to achieve
than I thought.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:19:38.260 --> 00:19:40.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I brought some liquor
to offer at your grave.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:19:41.220 --> 00:19:42.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would you like a drink?</b></Default>

c0000338
00:19:42.720 --> 00:19:44.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I gave the stuff up.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:19:44.810 --> 00:19:45.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:19:46.520 --> 00:19:48.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I doubt the Goddess
will forgive you.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:19:48.520 --> 00:19:50.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're far too close
to corpse-hood</b></Default>

c0000342
00:19:50.190 --> 00:19:51.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to clean up your act now.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:19:51.570 --> 00:19:52.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Heiter laughs]</b></Default>

c0000344
00:19:53.270 --> 00:19:56.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

c0000345
00:19:58.620 --> 00:20:00.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why, thank you, kind lady.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:20:00.410 --> 00:20:03.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

c0000347
00:20:05.840 --> 00:20:06.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who is she?</b></Default>

c0000348
00:20:07.090 --> 00:20:08.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her name is Fern.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:20:08.920 --> 00:20:11.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was orphaned by the wars
in the southern lands.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:20:13.040 --> 00:20:14.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My, how unexpected.</b></Default>

c0000351
00:20:14.920 --> 00:20:17.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've never thought you
the type to do charity</b></Default>

c0000352
00:20:17.100 --> 00:20:18.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for charity's sake.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:20:18.550 --> 00:20:19.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was always Himmel.</b></Default>

c0000354
00:20:20.470 --> 00:20:21.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:20:22.930 --> 00:20:25.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren, why did you come
visit me?</b></Default>

c0000356
00:20:26.020 --> 00:20:28.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had a few errands to run
in the holy city.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:20:28.690 --> 00:20:30.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I want to learn more
about those I have met</b></Default>

c0000358
00:20:30.650 --> 00:20:32.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and will meet on my travels.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:20:33.440 --> 00:20:34.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've done me much good,</b></Default>

c0000360
00:20:34.440 --> 00:20:36.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I came here
to repay my debts.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:20:36.450 --> 00:20:38.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I imagine your time
is running low.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:20:39.200 --> 00:20:40.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:20:42.030 --> 00:20:43.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In that case, I have a request.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:20:44.030 --> 00:20:45.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000365
00:20:45.320 --> 00:20:47.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Might you take on
an apprentice?</b></Default>

c0000366
00:20:49.080 --> 00:20:52.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fern has potential as a mage,
but needs adequate training.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:20:53.170 --> 00:20:55.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Will you bring her with you
and strengthen her skills?</b></Default>

c0000368
00:20:56.340 --> 00:20:59.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

c0000369
00:20:59.260 --> 00:21:00.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Forgive me, Heiter,</b></Default>

c0000370
00:21:00.890 --> 00:21:02.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I must draw a line.</b></Default>

c0000371
00:21:02.930 --> 00:21:04.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She'd only get in my way.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:21:05.430 --> 00:21:07.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We both know how often
apprentice mages</b></Default>

c0000373
00:21:07.600 --> 00:21:08.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>die in battle.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:21:10.100 --> 00:21:12.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will not send a child
my friend asked me</b></Default>

c0000375
00:21:12.190 --> 00:21:13.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to care for to her death.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:21:16.910 --> 00:21:17.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
Understood.</b></Default>

c0000377
00:21:18.360 --> 00:21:20.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have another favor in mind.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:21:21.360 --> 00:21:22.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000379
00:21:25.870 --> 00:21:27.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
This was unearthed</b></Default>

c0000380
00:21:27.080 --> 00:21:29.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the tomb of Ewig the Sage.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:21:29.580 --> 00:21:32.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Inside this grimoire,
there is said to be a wealth</b></Default>

c0000382
00:21:32.620 --> 00:21:35.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of lost spells,
with powers ranging</b></Default>

c0000383
00:21:35.080 --> 00:21:37.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from resurrection
to immortality.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:21:37.800 --> 00:21:40.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I find it hard to believe
that such magic exists.</b></Default>

c0000385
00:21:41.510 --> 00:21:42.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
That's part of the reason</b></Default>

c0000386
00:21:42.800 --> 00:21:44.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why I'd like you
to decipher it.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:21:45.340 --> 00:21:46.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Up for the challenge?</b></Default>

c0000388
00:21:47.020 --> 00:21:49.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The code is largely
symbol-based.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:21:49.310 --> 00:21:51.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The people of this era
had a penchant</b></Default>

c0000390
00:21:51.140 --> 00:21:52.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for such things.</b></Default>

c0000391
00:21:52.730 --> 00:21:54.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll need at least
five or six years.</b></Default>

c0000392
00:21:55.640 --> 00:21:56.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do what you can.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:21:57.780 --> 00:22:00.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why do you want these spells
deciphered in the first place?</b></Default>

c0000394
00:22:00.900 --> 00:22:03.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You told us that death
doesn't worry you.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:22:03.530 --> 00:22:05.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I said
I wasn't afraid to die,</b></Default>

c0000396
00:22:06.040 --> 00:22:07.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I may have been more concerned</b></Default>

c0000397
00:22:07.710 --> 00:22:10.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with my perceived courage
than the truth of my words.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:22:11.040 --> 00:22:12.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>More than that,</b></Default>

c0000399
00:22:12.330 --> 00:22:14.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my fear has grown
since we spoke on the matter.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:22:15.970 --> 00:22:19.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And even if immortality
is out of my grasp,</b></Default>

c0000401
00:22:20.220 --> 00:22:22.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not ready to go just yet.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:22:22.130 --> 00:22:23.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll take any more time
that I can.</b></Default>

c0000403
00:22:24.170 --> 00:22:28.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000404
00:22:28.230 --> 00:22:29.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you read the holy texts,</b></Default>

c0000405
00:22:30.020 --> 00:22:32.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you'll find instructions
to live a healthy life.</b></Default>

c0000406
00:22:32.390 --> 00:22:33.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What better
expression of health</b></Default>

c0000407
00:22:34.020 --> 00:22:35.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than a few more years?</b></Default>

c0000408
00:22:35.430 --> 00:22:38.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Miscreant of the cloth.
-[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000409
00:22:39.490 --> 00:22:42.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, and whenever you need
a break from your task,</b></Default>

c0000410
00:22:43.110 --> 00:22:46.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>do you mind teaching Fern
the magic that you see fit?</b></Default>

c0000411
00:22:46.750 --> 00:22:48.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As a priest,
I lack the knowledge</b></Default>

c0000412
00:22:48.910 --> 00:22:51.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to further her studies
in magery.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:22:51.870 --> 00:22:53.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right. That should be fine.</b></Default>

c0000414
00:22:54.910 --> 00:22:57.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000415
00:22:59.460 --> 00:23:01.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[leaves rustling]</b></Default>

c0000416
00:23:01.920 --> 00:23:03.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There you are.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:23:04.300 --> 00:23:06.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I could scarcely find
any trace of you.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:23:06.850 --> 00:23:08.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are the woods
your usual training grounds?</b></Default>

c0000419
00:23:09.140 --> 00:23:10.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
I know I can be hard to find,</b></Default>

c0000420
00:23:10.770 --> 00:23:12.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I didn't think
someone like you</b></Default>

c0000421
00:23:12.180 --> 00:23:13.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would have that same trouble.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:23:13.810 --> 00:23:15.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Master Heiter never knows
where I am.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:23:16.190 --> 00:23:18.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He says
I'm practically invisible.</b></Default>

c0000424
00:23:19.900 --> 00:23:22.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think that is
a very good thing, don't you?</b></Default>

c0000425
00:23:23.860 --> 00:23:24.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is indeed.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:23:25.070 --> 00:23:27.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000427
00:23:27.870 --> 00:23:28.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
It's true.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:23:29.620 --> 00:23:31.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can barely detect
her presence.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:23:32.410 --> 00:23:34.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her control over her mana
is exceptional.</b></Default>

c0000430
00:23:35.960 --> 00:23:38.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How much could she have
studied at such a young age?</b></Default>

c0000431
00:23:39.880 --> 00:23:41.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Master Heiter said,</b></Default>

c0000432
00:23:41.590 --> 00:23:43.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>once I'm able to blast
a hole in that rock,</b></Default>

c0000433
00:23:44.210 --> 00:23:45.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be a proper mage.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:23:46.010 --> 00:23:47.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000435
00:23:47.140 --> 00:23:48.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>His idea is a decent one.</b></Default>

c0000436
00:23:48.890 --> 00:23:51.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a...</b></Default>

c0000437
00:23:53.470 --> 00:23:55.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000438
00:23:55.850 --> 00:23:58.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My magic never makes it
to the other side.</b></Default>

c0000439
00:23:58.440 --> 00:23:59.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It just won't reach.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:24:00.610 --> 00:24:01.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see the issue.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:24:02.320 --> 00:24:04.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you know any ways
I can train this skill?</b></Default>

c0000442
00:24:05.860 --> 00:24:08.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, but can I ask you
something first?</b></Default>

c0000443
00:24:09.580 --> 00:24:10.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you like magic?</b></Default>

c0000444
00:24:11.580 --> 00:24:13.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I like it somewhat, I guess.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:24:14.240 --> 00:24:15.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000446
00:24:16.130 --> 00:24:17.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
In that, we're alike.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:25:50.300 --> 00:25:51.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
Is Fern's training</b></Default>

c0000448
00:25:51.720 --> 00:25:52.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-coming along smoothly?
-Such a hero</b></Default>

c0000449
00:25:53.050 --> 00:25:54.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>should be revered,
not left to crumble.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:25:55.050 --> 00:25:56.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] But they're
well worth looking for.</b></Default>

c0000451
00:25:56.520 --> 00:25:57.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] I'd like to show
you them someday.</b></Default>

c0000452
00:25:57.940 --> 00:25:59.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
It didn't have to be magic.</b></Default>

